article_id:3273,category_name:News,title_name:A Platinum Showcase Is Coming Soon! 5★ Gala Dragalia Adventurer Guaranteed!,image_path:,message:<div>A Platinum Showcase starts on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1666936800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>The Platinum Showcase is a limited summon showcase that works similarly to a tenfold summon in that one summon will get you 10 results. The difference between a regular tenfold summon and this Platinum Showcase is that a 5★ Gala adventurer available at the start of this summon showcase is guaranteed to appear.</div><div><br></div><div>To see the details of the adventurers who appear in this Platinum Showcase, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select the Platinum Showcase and check the Appearance Rates section.</div><div><br></div><div>During the availability period, players are limited to doing the Platinum Showcase summon five times, and these summons can only be performed with diamantium (purchase required).</div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for the Platinum Showcase:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1666936800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1667368799"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the 5★ adventurers eligible to appear as the guaranteed 5★ summon below.</div><div><br></div><div>
